<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
       <p><a href="https://www.outfitadditions.com"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/oamktplace/2014logo.jpg"></a></p>
       <p>
         Dear <%= @order.seller.name %>, <br><br>You have a new order at Outfit Additions. <br><br>
         <b>Product ID:</b> <%= @order.listingsku %><br>
         <b>Product name:</b> <%= @order.listingname %><br>
         <b>Sold for:</b>  <%= number_to_currency(@order.price_sold)  %><br>
         <b>Seller Price (after fees):</b><%= number_to_currency(@order.seller_payment) %>
       </p>

          <b>Ship the item to: </b><br>
           <%= @order.shipname %><br>
           <%= if !@order.shipcompany.blank? then @order.shipcompany end %><% if !@order.shipcompany.blank? %><br><% end %>
           <%= @order.shipaddress %><br>
           <%= if !@order.shipaddress2.blank? then @order.shipaddress2 end %><% if !@order.shipaddress2.blank? %><br><% end %>
           <%= @order.shipcity %><br>
           <%= "#{@order.shipstate}, #{@order.shipzip}" %><br>
           Customer email: <%= @buyer.email %><br>
           <% if !@order.comments.blank? %>
              <b>Customer comments:</b> <%= @order.comments %><br>
          <% end %>

       <p><b>Shipping process: </b>If the item is in stock, please ship this order within 1-2 business days. If you marked the item as 'made to order', please ship within the timeframe you mentioned in the listing. 
        <ul>
          <li>Go to your <%= link_to "Manage Sales", sales_path %> page and print the invoice.</li>
          <li>After shipping the item, please enter your carrier and tracking information against the order row on the same page. 
          <li>Then click on the confirm shipment button to confirm your shipment. This sends an email to the customer confirming shipment and includes the tracking info that was entered.</li>
        </ul>

       <p>To check sales details and manage your account, please login at <%= @url %>. If you have any questions, please email us at service@outfitadditions.com.</p>

       <p>--The Outfit Additions team</p>
    
  </body>
</html>